{
  "stem": "15694.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it's not a great distance, and the rest of the camp I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Where I worked in-- in the beginning, I didn't know much either.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Sort of I-- it's-- and company, I didn't go visiting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I didn't see only-- I think only once I see the-- the-- his wife.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "During all the 10 months I was in this camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "No-- no social visits or anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Now, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I walked along the wire towards the kitchen, where I hoped to meet another policeman, which I knew the one, Salz.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The one who was hanging that fellow, and the one who gave me food a couple of times.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There was a hole in the-- in the wire between the workshop area.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I went into the kitchen, back entrance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Nobody there.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "On the other hand, before I went out, I swiped the kitchen-- a chef's hat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Donned it, put it on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And marched that way with the-- with the white pack, you know, rucksack, so to say, on my back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Towards where I thought was the-- remembered something where the police station was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody stopped me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went inside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there somebody on duty asked where Sygmund was, my cousin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said he wasn't here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Could I wait?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I took off my hat, and I was sitting there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After a while, the man, said, look.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe it's better that you go back to work, because if you're found here, you know what could happen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, I can't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I'll tell you what I want.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I told you that my father is in the what I-- what I was just sort of named the mini camp, and I want to go in or to get somebody to come out.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
